@startuml
title Widget Layout - Practical Flow

skinparam ParticipantPadding 8

actor "User widget" as UserWidget
participant "Parent Widget" as Parent
participant "Child Widget" as Child
participant "UpdateModule" as UpdateModule
participant "RenderUnitBuilder" as Builder

UserWidget -> Parent : create child widgets
Parent -> Child : owns through parent-child tree

loop each update tick
	UpdateModule -> Parent : update(tick)
	Parent -> Parent : run custom update
	Parent -> Child : update(tick)
	Child -> Child : run custom update
end

alt widget geometry changes
	Parent -> Child : notify inherited geometry
	Child -> Child : recompute local/global area
end

loop render snapshot rebuild
	Parent -> Builder : append own drawing
	Parent -> Child : appendRenderUnits(builder)
	Child -> Builder : append child drawing
end

note over Parent,Child
User widgets customize behavior by overriding event,
update, and render-unit creation hooks.
end note

@enduml
